<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>欢迎加入</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .welcome p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #718096;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 40px;
        }
        
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .feature {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .feature h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .feature p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .info-section {
            background-color: #edf2f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .info-section h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .info-section p {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer .company {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 注册成功</h1>
            <p>欢迎加入我们的大家庭</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome">
                <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
                <h2>恭喜您，<%= username %>！</h2>
                <p>您的账户已成功创建并验证，现在可以开始使用我们的服务了</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
                    <h4>安全保障</h4>
                    <p>多重安全验证保护您的账户</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                    <h4>高效管理</h4>
                    <p>强大的后台管理功能</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                    <h4>数据分析</h4>
                    <p>详细的数据统计和分析</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h4>精准控制</h4>
                    <p>灵活的权限管理系统</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= loginUrl || '#' %>" class="btn">立即登录</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>📋 账户信息</h3>
                <p><strong>用户名：</strong><%= username %></p>
                <p><strong>邮箱：</strong><%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>注册时间：</strong><%= new Date().toLocaleString('zh-CN') %></p>
                <p><strong>账户状态：</strong>已激活</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>💡 使用提示</h3>
                <p>• 请妥善保管您的登录凭据</p>
                <p>• 建议定期更新密码以确保安全</p>
                <p>• 如有任何问题，请联系客服支持</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="company">商城管理系统</p>
            <p>感谢您的信任与支持</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0;">
                © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> 版权所有
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>